Block difficulty reward:
  - if a block is mined with double the current difficulty (e.g 8 zeros instead of 4), 
  - mint 3 times the normal reward to the user
Creating currency based on timestamp:
  - if a block is mined at exactly 11:11:11 am on a Monday in pacific time 
  _ mint 11 times the current reward for user
Destroying based on gas cost:
  - if the transactions of past 10 gas costs are over 10% of transaction amount
  - burn 10% of the next user's transaction

